CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1778764275
OL,3,CPlaque unveiled at home of first
OL,4,CEnglish women to work as professional
OL,5,Cartist
OL,7,FA national blue plaque has been
OL,8,Funveiled at the home of Mary Beale to
OL,9,Frecognise her achievement as one of
OL,10,Fthe first English women to work as a
OL,11,Fprofessional artist.
OL,13,FHistoric England has installed the
OL,14,Fplaque at Allbrook Farmhouse in
OL,15,FEastleigh, Hampshire, to mark the
OL,16,Fcareer of the portrait painter who
OL,17,Flived from 1633 to 1699 and has been
OL,18,Fdescribed as "ahead of her time".
OL,26,@zD@NOUzD@`O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
