PN,41508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1778764275
OL,3,CPlaque unveiled at home of first
OL,4,CEnglish women to work as professional
OL,5,Cartist
OL,7,F"She did for this stratum of society
OL,8,Fwhat Sir Peter Lely did for the
OL,9,Faristocracy."
OL,11,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,12,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,13,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,14,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,15,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,16,Fbelow...
